title: My 10 Books - April 2016 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 books for the month:

01. 300+ Successful Business Letters for All Occasions (2nd Ed) by Alan Bond
02. Elements of Modern Algebra (7th Ed) by Linda Gilbert
03. Indian Head Massage (3rd Ed) by Helen McGuinness
04. Man's Unconquerable Mind by Gilbert Highet
05. Recipes and Tips for Healthy, Thrifty Meals by US Dept. for Agriculture
06. Seven Wonders of Medicine by Karen Gunnison Ballen
07. The Britannica Guide to the History of Mathematics by Erik Gregersen
08. Touch Me There! - A Hands-On Guide to Your Orgasmic Hot Spots by M.S. Yvonne K Fulbright
09. Wisden on the Ashes - The Authoritative Story of Cricket's Greatest Rivalry by Steven Lynch
10. Eco-Sex - Go Green Between the Sheets and Make Your Love Life Sustainable by Stefanie Iris Weiss
